show.description: To save her ailing grandmother, she made an unthinkable sacrifice — selling herself for three hundred thousand Yuan. Bound by a contract, she married a complete stranger. But what began as an act of desperation soon spiraled into a whirlwind of unexpected trials that would change her destiny forever.
